func = Function(([T, List(T)], Set(T)), ([Set(List(T))], Integer), ([Set(T),
    List(T)], T))
assert func.takes_arguments(args) == return_type
pytest.mark.parametrize('args, return_type', [([Set(Integer), List(Set(
    Integer))], Set(Set(Integer))), ([Real, List(Real)], Set(Real)), ([Set(
    List(Bool))], Integer), ([Set(Color), List(Color)], Color), ([Color,
    List(Side)], None), ([Set(Side), List(Color)], None)])
